[ParsedRows, parsedRows](parser-dsl-values-lib.ssc)

[ParseOk](std/parsing/core.ssc)

# Parser extension and ordinary collection dispatch

```scalascript
parsedRows() match
  case ParseOk(ParsedRows(rows), rest, pos) =>
    val rendered = rows.asInstanceOf[List[Any]].map(row =>
      row._1.toString + ":" + row._2
    ).mkString("|")
    println(rendered)
  case _ => println("failed")
```
